attributes.name: instanceId
attributes.description: Internal identifier of the storageProcessor instance.

attributes.name: id
attributes.description: Unique identifier of the storageProcessor instance.

attributes.name: parent
attributes.description: Resource type and unique identifier for the SP's parent enclosure.

attributes.name: health
attributes.description: Health information for the SP, as defined by the health resource type.

attributes.name: operationalStatus
attributes.description: Operational statuses for the SP.

attributes.name: needsReplacement
attributes.description:
Indicates whether the SP needs replacement. Values are:
  • true - SP needs replacement.
  • false - SP does not need replacement.

attributes.name: isRescueMode
attributes.description:
Indicates whether the SP is in Service Mode. Values are:
  • true - SP is in Service Mode.
  • false - SP is not in Service Mode.

attributes.name: model
attributes.description: Manufacturer's model number for the SP.

attributes.name: slotNumber
attributes.description: Slot where the SP is located in the parent enclosure.

attributes.name: name
attributes.description: SP name.

attributes.name: emcPartNumber
attributes.description: EMC part number for the SP.

attributes.name: emcSerialNumber
attributes.description: EMC serial number for the SP.

attributes.name: manufacturer
attributes.description: Manufacturer of the SP.

attributes.name: vendorPartNumber
attributes.description: Vendor part number for the SP.

attributes.name: vendorSerialNumber
attributes.description: Vendor serial number for the SP.

attributes.name: sasExpanderVersion
attributes.description: Version number of the SAS Expander associated with the SP.

attributes.name: biosFirmwareRevision
attributes.description: Version number of the SP BIOS.

attributes.name: postFirmwareRevision
attributes.description: Version number of the SP Power-On Self-Test software.

attributes.name: memorySize
attributes.description: SP RAM size.

attributes.name: parentDpe
attributes.description: Parent Disk Processor Enclosure (DPE) of the storage processor.
